c: 18
v: 57
t: "Kodiwolakwakwambirindanikuposa munthu amene akakumbutsidwa mavesi a Ambuye wake iye amawakana ndi kuiwala zimene manja ake atsogoza? Ife taika zophimba mitima yawo kuti asazindikire ndipo tatseka m’makutu mwawo. Ndipo ngati iwe utawaitana iwo kuti atsatire njira yoyenera, iwo sadzatsogozedwa"